A simple and intuitive farm management tool built with HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and vanilla JavaScript.

The app allows farmers to record daily yields for different animals (such as cows, goats, and chickens) through a responsive web form. Totals are automatically calculated and displayed in real time.

A secondary page simulates a database view, listing all entries to provide a printable overview of daily production.

